2. **Audience segments** — which sub-sectors of the industry should the page cover? Offer 4 options, allow multi-select. *Examples for cyber: product startups Series A–C / enterprise & GRC / MSSPs / deeptech & national security. For deeptech: defence-tech / battery & EV / advanced manufacturing / energy & nuclear / robotics & medical AI / frontier & climate.*
3. **Case studies** — real clients, placeholders, "currently shipping", or a mix? Always recommend the mix — real clients where Everything Design has shipped, "currently shipping" cards for active engagements, placeholders only when the user has no clients in the category.

